  WHILE LOOP -

  - While loop is an entry contol loop. that repatedly executes a block of codes , as long as the given condition remains true, (While loop is used in situation where we do not know the exact number of iltrations of the loop)

DO and While -

- Do while loop is an exit control loop that repatedly execute a block of codes atleast ones
and countinues executing as long as a given condition remains true.

